title: Fox (2013) [MP3]
description:
Dear listener,

We want to thank you for choosing to listen to our self-titled debut album.
If you like what you hear, feel free to check us out at our website listed below!

Fox is an original blues rock trio from Kalamazoo, Michigan. We've been playing
together for about two years, developing our sound and wild stage antics along the way.

Enjoy!

Sincerely,


Chris Sinclair
John Lawrence
Carman Goodrich
